Package: ggdfe
Title: A Theme for ggplot in Department for Education House Style
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sam", "Cooke", ,"sam.cooke@education.gov.uk", role = c("aut","cre"))
    )
Description: A package to apply the house style of the Department
    for Education to ggplot, including colours and themes, for consistent
    reproducable charting for R users at DfE.
